00:33:27,570 --> 00:33:31,200
Don't say anything
if you don't know how to.

517
00:33:32,750 --> 00:33:37,730
I think Gao Ting and Nan Xi are kings.

518
00:33:37,810 --> 00:33:39,610
A mountain cannot tolerate two tigers.

519
00:33:39,690 --> 00:33:41,250
Just like meat buns.

520
00:33:41,330 --> 00:33:43,450
You can't stuff two big pieces
at the same time.

521
00:33:43,530 --> 00:33:47,430
Fat Tiger, why is all that you say
related to food?

522
00:33:47,510 --> 00:33:51,310
I'm really worried
about passing Nan Xi to you.

523
00:33:51,390 --> 00:33:55,170
Swordswoman, don't worry, we are a team.

524
00:33:55,250 --> 00:33:59,720
As long as I, Fat Tiger, have a bite,
Nan Xi won't starve.
